select index_name, column_name from INFORMATION_SCHEMA.SYSTEM_INDEXINFO idx where not exists ( select 1 from INFORMATION_SCHEMA.table_constraints cons where idx.table_name=cons.table_name and index_name=cons.constraint_name or RIGHT(index_name,length(index_name)-8) like concat(cons.constraint_name,'%')) and table_name=:TABLE
